{"tid":1036892,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［NBA有趣統計］原來得5個球員keep到","createTime":"2019-02-25T14:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T09:51:24.000Z","uid":65686,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"55fc8196f3d8dbced26fb94860ee5489d2c99735","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"啱無聊查左下啲stats發覺，所有現役打超過400場比賽嘅球員之中，只有5位係<span style=\"color: red;\">一直正選出場，從未打過後備</span>：<br />\n<br />\n1. Chris Paul 928場<br />\n2. Kevin Durant 830場<br />\n3. Blake Griffin 585場<br />\n4. Damian Lillard 527場<br />\n5. Kyrie Irving 490場<br />\n<br />\n打得400場都有至少5個賽季，同埋其實都唔止係現役球員，包含埋退役球員都係只有呢5位，大家點睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3f339bf8b407a7c651d0ce426eabdc59092af9","tid":1036892,"uid":1713,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"Lbj 一開頭係做ricky davis 後備"},{"pid":"df54a3436d5eb157f4e012f6a42801e18abc147a","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"7e3f339bf8b407a7c651d0ce426eabdc59092af9","tid":1036892,"uid":1713,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"Lbj 一開頭係做ricky davis 後備"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />LBJ生涯只有一場後備，係幫Varejao"},{"pid":"ebe2c1cf8037ffe5662f744e7d8a683bc7dea873","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"講返啲比較可惜嘅球員：<br />\n<br />\nCarmelo Anthony一直都係球隊大佬，即使轉會雷霆都不甘讓位打後備。直到今季來左火箭，畀教練D&rsquo;Antoni洗左腦打左8場後備，而家冇人要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7f9f4712ef2a1b581d1ea641b19c0ad0c09998","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"Tim Duncan: 3次<br />\n1. 04年傷膝，復出戰為安全起見，教練普波域治決定畀鄧肯打後備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 09-10賽季，教練普波域治覺得需要改變一下，就安排鄧肯打後備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 15-16賽季，面對勇士，教練普波域治變陣應對，安排鄧肯打後備，最終戰勝勇士，呢1場都係勇士成個賽季輸嘅9場波嘅其中1場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e51ce2ff08e4d28353931dc2c82c901109cfefc","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"Dwight Howard : 1次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2006年3月22日，魔術當晚主場迎戰紐約力搏。侯活由於塞車而缺席左下午嘅訓練，教練為左懲罰佢，決定撳佢去後備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab3173007d9d62c5ba0702620d20ac007dfcd3e","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"Al Horford : 4次<br />\n<br />\n估唔到Horford先得4場咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係集中喺rookie season"},{"pid":"33553e265978e4b67b475e74412c5d17ede25b3b","tid":1036892,"uid":84519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"Westbrook 原來都有打後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cb9f9ce85f93d0413bac5d8d020b0b96a4d2d4","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"Karl Malone : 4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢4次全部都發生喺rookie season。同時Karl Malone仲係正選次數（1471場）嘅紀錄保持者，奴域司機1441場緊追其後，但今季先得一場正選，睇來都唔會破到。"},{"pid":"3c7655f4693e154b36239adbf81a60e82ae696a4","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"David Robinson : 2次<br />\n<br />\n海軍上將頭2個賽季各後備出場1次。"},{"pid":"daaf25e8260e5a9632aac30e0aff50aad0dfb105","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02cb9f9ce85f93d0413bac5d8d020b0b96a4d2d4","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"Karl Malone : 4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢4次全部都發生喺rookie season。同時Karl Malone仲係正選次數（1471場）嘅紀錄保持者，奴域司機1441場緊追其後，但今季先得一場正選，睇來都唔會破到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Malone係5次"},{"pid":"0eeae3110746380305a8c228e887c1aa7be871e0","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"Brad Daugherty: 2 次<br />\n<br />\n86年狀元，騎士揀中，因為嚴重背傷生涯只有8年。"},{"pid":"82f7294e246bc5cc1582be31c2ff9bf28cc1bf43","tid":1036892,"uid":95542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"姚明呢？"},{"pid":"a24afb646ffd7bfb6fa51897bfccd1c1fcd346c6","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82f7294e246bc5cc1582be31c2ff9bf28cc1bf43","tid":1036892,"uid":95542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"姚明呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"姚明只有10場後備出場，都喺rookie season。即使係姚明嘅debut，都係後備出場。就算係狀元，始終都要適應。"},{"pid":"776651796dab6e3a8c4ce97cb5c6e0ccdae15b91","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:28:36.000Z","msg":"Curry有6場後備，3場喺rookie season，3場係傷癒復出。"},{"pid":"59fdeafbc7ab480267985844d25848d4a0e36382","tid":1036892,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"AD有5場，同Curry嘅情形差唔多"},{"pid":"8b205783534b69d883559b0c67ea5f1f9b8bf